# Cargo build artifacts — any peer workspace.
# Previously this was `/main/target` (old single-workspace shape).
# Since the `refactor: restructure from Multi-Feature workspace to
# Multi-Project peers` move (commit 6e35231), every top-level peer
# (gateway/, controlroom/, http/, …) has its own target/ tree.
**/target/

# Cargo lockfiles for peer workspaces. Convention on this repo is
# that library peers don't commit Cargo.lock (gateway/Cargo.lock
# has been untracked since the peers refactor). Bin crates that
# need reproducible installs can opt in by un-gitignoring their
# own `<peer>/Cargo.lock`.
**/Cargo.lock

*.swp
.DS_Store
